McCRUDEN, Respondent, v. ROCHESTER RY. CO., Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by Bridget McGruden against the Rochester Railway Company.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. J., and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment and order appealed from affirmed, on opinion of Rumsey, J., at the circuit. 25 N. Y. Supp. 114.
